#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. This guide is maintained in the main Quarkus repository
#. and pull requests should be submitted there:
#. https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/tree/main/docs/src/main/asciidoc
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using OpenTelemetry"
msgstr "使用OpenTelemetry"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This guide explains how your Quarkus application can utilize https://opentelemetry.io/[OpenTelemetry] (OTel) to provide\n"
"Observability for interactive web applications."
msgstr "本指南介绍了您的 Quarkus 应用程序如何利用 link:https://opentelemetry.io/[OpenTelemetry] （OTel）为交互式 Web 应用程序提供可观测性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "On this page we show the signal independent features of the extension."
msgstr "在本页面中，我们将介绍该扩展程序中与信号无关的功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This document is part of the xref:observability.adoc[Observability in Quarkus reference guide] which features this and other observability related components."
msgstr "本文档是《 xref:observability.adoc[Quarkus 可观测性参考指南] 》的一部分，该指南介绍了本组件以及其他与可观测性相关的组件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The old OpenTelemetry guide has been split into this generic guide, the xref:opentelemetry-tracing.adoc[OpenTelemetry Tracing Guide], the new xref:opentelemetry-metrics.adoc[OpenTelemetry Metrics Guide] and the xref:opentelemetry-logging.adoc[OpenTelemetry Logging Guide]."
msgstr "旧版的 OpenTelemetry 指南现已拆分为本通用指南、《 xref:opentelemetry-tracing.adoc[OpenTelemetry 追踪指南] 》、新版《 xref:opentelemetry-metrics.adoc[OpenTelemetry 指标指南] 》以及《 xref:opentelemetry-logging.adoc[OpenTelemetry 日志指南] 》。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The use of *the https://opentelemetry.io/docs/instrumentation/java/automatic/[OpenTelemetry Agent] is not needed nor recommended*. Quarkus Extensions and the libraries they provide, are directly instrumented. That agent doesn't work with native mode."
msgstr "*无需也不建议* 使用 *link:https://opentelemetry.io/docs/instrumentation/java/automatic/[OpenTelemetry 代理]* 。Quarkus 扩展及其提供的库已直接进行了性能监控配置。该代理不支持原生模式。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://opentelemetry.io/docs/what-is-opentelemetry/[OpenTelemetry] is an Observability framework and toolkit designed to create and manage telemetry data such as traces, metrics, and logs. Crucially, OpenTelemetry is vendor- and tool-agnostic."
msgstr "link:https://opentelemetry.io/docs/what-is-opentelemetry/[OpenTelemetry] 是一个可观测性框架和工具包，旨在创建和管理追踪、指标和日志等遥测数据。最重要的是，OpenTelemetry 具有供应商和工具中立性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus provides manual and automatic instrumentation for tracing and manual instrumentation capabilities for metrics."
msgstr "Quarkus 提供了用于跟踪的手动和自动仪器化功能，以及用于指标的手动仪器化功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This will allow Quarkus based applications to be observable by tools and services supporting OpenTelemetry."
msgstr "这将使基于 Quarkus 的应用程序能够被支持 OpenTelemetry 的工具和服务进行可观测。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Automatic metrics instrumentation in Quarkus is done by the xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[Quarkus Micrometer extension]."
msgstr "Quarkus 中的自动指标instrumentation由 xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[Quarkus Micrometer 扩展] 实现。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The xref:telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc[quarkus-micrometer-opentelemetry] extension enables the use and export of Micrometer metrics via OpenTelemetry."
msgstr "xref:telemetry-micrometer-to-opentelemetry.adoc[quarkus-micrometer-opentelemetry] 扩展支持通过 OpenTelemetry 使用和导出 Micrometer 指标。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus supports the OpenTelemetry Autoconfiguration. The configurations match what you can see at\n"
"https://opentelemetry.io/docs/languages/java/configuration/[OpenTelemetry SDK Autoconfigure]\n"
"with the `quarkus.*` prefix."
msgstr "Quarkus 支持 OpenTelemetry 自动配置。这些配置与 link:https://opentelemetry.io/docs/languages/java/configuration/[OpenTelemetry SDK 自动配置中] 显示的内容一致，只是前缀改为 `quarkus.*` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This guide provides a crosscutting explanation of the OpenTelemetry extension and how to use it. If you need details about any particular signal (tracing or metrics), please refer to the signal specific guide."
msgstr "本指南对 OpenTelemetry 扩展及其使用方法进行了通用的说明。如果您需要了解任何特定信号（追踪或指标）的详细信息，请参阅相应的信号指南。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "With the introduction of OpenTelemetry Metrics, the original, single page guide had to be split according to signal types, as follows:"
msgstr "随着 OpenTelemetry Metrics 的推出，原有的单页指南不得不根据信号类型进行拆分，具体如下："

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "xref:opentelemetry-tracing.adoc[OpenTelemetry Tracing Guide]"
msgstr "xref:opentelemetry-tracing.adoc[OpenTelemetry 追踪指南]"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The tracing functionality is supported and *on* by default."
msgstr "支持跟踪功能，且该功能默认 *处于启用状态* 。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc
#, fuzzy
